-- Autonomy Lowers Full-Year Revenue Guidance on `Prudent' Forecast Approach
-- B y   P e t e r   B r a n t o n
-- 2010-10-06T10:21:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-06/autonomy-lowers-full-year-revenue-guidance-on-prudent-forecast-approach.html
Autonomy Corp. said it will take a
“prudent approach” to forecasting and plans to review its
internal model for the full year with a revenue reduction of
around 3 percent “on current consensus and commensurate changes
to other parameters.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter Branton at 
 pbranton@bloomberg.net  